is the first of five to be announced from the region.
Matra has targeted Korea, Singapore and Malaysia as priority areas for its
defence activity and has opened sales offices in New Delhi, Hong Kong,
Seoul, Singapore, and Beijing.
Mr Gut said Goldstar and other South Korean partners will carry out roughly
25 per cent of the work on the Mistral missiles. The contract also includes
