FT  21 JAN 92 / UK Company News: CSG expands in north of England
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Corporate Services Group, the USM-quoted recruitment company,has acquired
Forward Recruitment Consultants, based in the north of England, from Vedior
International for an undisclosed sum.
