sensitivity', writes Raymond Hughes.
Five banks have claimed ownership of most of the stake, which is also
claimed by Macmillan, as collateral for loans extended to companies within
the Maxwell empire.
Asking for the application to be heard in camera, Mr David Oliver QC, for
